data.description: Nestled in the gated community of Fountain Lakes, this immaculately remodeled home is located on a lush, oversized lot. Pristine and IMMACULATELY REMODELED, this home is completely MOVE-IN READY! Buyers have the option of keeping all the furniture and electronics that are seen in the photos. The two car garage was recently coated with a three part industrial epoxy to create a GORGEOUS finish. The home will also be sold with a 22,000 watt generator that can power the entire home by plugging into the electrical panel.  Both the A/C and roof are just under a year old. The tropical and beautifully landscaped backyard provides privacy and plenty of room to entertain and enjoy.  Fountain Lakes is a highly sought after community as HOA fees and amenities, including golf, tennis, and pickleball, are unbeatable. Conveniently located in the heart of Estero, between Fort Myers and Naples, this home offers quick access to fantastic shopping, restaurants, beautiful beaches, schools, the airport, and hospitals. This gem won't last long. Make your offer TODAY!
